### Component Definition

```rust
#[component]
fn ComponentName() -> Element {
    // Component logic here
    rsx! {
        // JSX content
    }
}
```

### Signal Usage

```rust
// Initialize
let mut count = use_signal(|| 0);

// Read
let current = count();

// Update
count.set(count() + 1);
```

### Event Handlers

```rust
// Inline handler
onclick: move |_| {
    // action
}

// Handler with parameter
onclick: move |e| {
    title.set(e.value())
}
```

### Conditional Rendering

```rust
// Simple if
if condition() {
    rsx! { div { "Content" } }
}

// If-else pattern
if condition() {
    rsx! { div { "True" } }
} else {
    rsx! { div { "False" } }
}
```

### List Rendering

```rust
// Simple list
for item in items().iter() {
    ItemComponent { item: item.clone() }
}

// With filter
for item in items().iter().filter(|i| i.active) {
    ItemComponent { item: item.clone() }
}
```

## ğŸ”¤ Naming Conventions

### Components
- `PascalCase`: `App`, `ReminderCard`, `AddReminderForm`

### Functions
- `snake_case`: `load_reminders`, `save_reminders`

### Variables
- `snake_case`: `reminders`, `show_form`, `filter`

### Constants
- `UPPER_CASE`: `CACHE_NAME`, `MAX_ITEMS`

### Types
- `PascalCase`: `Reminder`, `ReminderStatus`

